COMFORT XML

A wrapper around W3C DOM to create a Java like XML API.

    Source: http://github.com/bigeasy/comfort-xml/tree/master
    Documentation: http://wiki.github.com/bigeasy/comfort-io

    Issues: http://bigeasy.lighthouseapp.com/projects/51853

    Contact: alan@blogometer.com

PURPOSE

Using XML shouldn't be a punishment. W3C DOM was brought to us when software
interfaces as contracts was the way of looking things, and the contract put
forward by W3C DOM is about as equitable as a pay day loan.
